ZCAM uses C2PA as its container format but adds hardware-backed guarantees that C2PA alone cannot provide.
Where C2PA tracks history with any signing key, ZCAM guarantees the photo was captured on a specific device using keys that can&#x27;t be extracted or forged. This transforms C2PA from a provenance system into an authenticity system.
